definitions.definition: Not real or substantial ; having no actual presence in reality; lacking the characteristics of reality.
very impressive ; amazing ; unbelievable ; incredible ; larger or more fantastic than typical of real life.
examples: The video includes unreal footage of an eight-metre wave.
I just had an unreal hamburger.

main_definition: Not real or substantial ; having no actual presence in reality; lacking the characteristics of reality.
secondary_definitions: ( informal ) very impressive ; amazing ; unbelievable ; incredible ; larger or more fantastic than typical of real life.
